rt: 28 tool calls (Bash: 10, Read: 13, Edit: 6, Grep: 4, Glob: 1, Skill: 1). 17 unique files. No redundancy.\n30\t\n31\t### 15-3-driver-capability-matrix-routing-hints — verify (2026-04-03T13:40)\n32\t\n33\t- **AGENTS.md staleness:** `src/lib/AGENTS.md` and `src/lib/agents/AGENTS.md` missing `capability-check.ts`. Fixed.\n34\t- **Pre-existing lint error:** `require-yield` in workflow-engine.test.ts:170 — not from story 15-3.\n35\t- **Pre-existing 300-line violations:** codex.ts (333), opencode.ts (339) from stories 12-1/12-2. This story added 1 line each.\n36\t- **Observation:** `codeharness drivers` CLI works in both pretty-print and JSON modes.\n37\t- ALL_PASS: 12/12 ACs verified. `codeharness verify` passes after AGENTS.md fix.\n38\t\n39\tToken Report: 15 tool calls (Bash: 11, Read: 1, Write: 1, Grep: 1, Glob: 2). 1 unique file. Minor redundancy (2 duplicate CLI runs).\n40\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9c9fe147-c536-4d36-9f64-8249f0c68839","uuid":"f6f1f2d7-8b76-421b-99cb-93e9c82a6d29","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:36:23.814Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03 (Session 15)\n\n### 15-3-driver-capability-matrix-routing-hints — create-story (2026-04-03T13:17)\n\n- **No project-context.md found.** Workflow references it but none exists. Not a blocker.\n- **Config.yaml path mismatch.** `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` doesn't exist, actual is `_bmad/config.yaml`.\n- **Risk: ACs #3 and #4 (`codeharness drivers` CLI) are runtime-provable** — require binary invocation.\n- **Risk: costTier simplification** — uses integer tiers (1/2/3) not real $ costs. May need revisiting.\n- **Observation:** Last story in sprint. After this, all epics done.\n- 2 runtime-provable ACs, 10 test-provable ACs.\n\nToken Report: 26 tool calls (Bash: 2, Read: 13, Grep: 9, Write: 1, Glob: 4, Skill: 1). 15 unique files. No redundancy.\