, boolean>` instead of `Partial<DriverCapabilities>`. Fixed.","-- **MEDIUM: Duplicate imports** in `drivers.ts` and `capability-check.ts`. Consolidated.","-- **MEDIUM: Missing test** for JSON vs pretty-print output formatting in `drivers.test.ts`. Added.","-- **LOW (not fixed): `DRIVER_DESCRIPTIONS` static map** could go stale if new driver added.","-- **LOW (not fixed): `Record<string, unknown>` cast** in `suggestCheaperDriver`.","-- Coverage: 96.86% overall, all 173 files above 80% floor. 4649 tests pass.","-","-Token Report: 28 tool calls (Bash: 10, Read: 13, Edit: 6, Grep: 4, Glob: 1, Skill: 1). 17 unique files. No redundancy.","-","-### 15-3-driver-capability-matrix-routing-hints — verify (2026-04-03T13:40)","-","-- **AGENTS.md staleness:** `src/lib/AGENTS.md` and `src/lib/agents/AGENTS.md` missing `capability-check.ts`. Fixed.","-- **Pre-existing lint error:** `require-yield` in workflow-engine.test.ts:170 — not from story 15-3.","-- **Pre-existing 300-line violations:** codex.ts (333), opencode.ts (339) from stories 12-1/12-2. This story added 1 line each.","-- **Observation:** `codeharness drivers` CLI works in both pretty-print and JSON modes.","-- ALL_PASS: 12/12 ACs verified. `codeharness verify` passes after AGENTS.md fix.","-","-Token Report: 15 tool calls (Bash: 11, Read: 1, Write: 1, Grep: 1, Glob: 2). 1 unique file. Minor redundancy (2 duplicate CLI runs).","+# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03"]}],"originalFile":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03 (Session 15)\n\n### 15-3-driver-capability-matrix-routing-hints — create-story (2026-04-03T13:17)\n\n- **No project-context.md found.** Workflow references it but none exists. Not a blocker.\n- **Config.yaml path mismatch.** `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` doesn't exist, actual is `_bmad/config.yaml`.\n- **Risk: ACs #3 and #4 (`codeharness drivers` CLI) are runtime-provable** — require binary invocation.\n- **Risk: costTier simplification** — uses integer tiers (1/2/3) not real $ costs. May need revisiting.\n- **Observation:** Last story in sprint. After this, all epics done.\n- 2 runtime-provable ACs, 10 test-provable ACs.\n\nToken Report: 26 tool calls (Bash: 2, Read: 13, Grep: 9, Write: 1, Glob: 4, Skill: 1). 15 unique files. No redundancy.\n\n### 15-3-driver-capability-matrix-routing-hints — dev-story (2026-04-03T13:26)\n\nNo issues reported. Build passes, 4648 tests across 172 files, zero regressions.\n\nToken Report: 39 tool calls (Bash: 8, Read: 14, Edit: 20, Grep: 6, Write: 3, Glob: 1). 18 unique files, 21 total reads. No redundancy.\n\n### 15-3-driver-capability-matrix-routing-hints — code-review (2026-04-03T13:33)\n\n- **HIGH: Wrong type annotation** in `capability-check.ts` — `Record<string, boolean>` instead of `Partial<DriverCapabilities>`. Fixed.\n- **MEDIUM: Duplicate imports** in `drivers.ts` and `capability-check.ts`. Consolidated.\n- **MEDIUM: Missing test** for JSON vs pretty-print output formatting in `drivers.test.ts`. Added.\n- **LOW (not fixed): `DRIVER_DESCRIPTIONS` static map** could go stale if new driver added.\n- **LOW (not fixed): `Record<string, unknown>` cast** in `suggestCheaperDriver`.\n- Coverage: 96.86% overall, all 173 files above 80% floor. 4649 tests pass.\n\nToken Report: 28 tool calls (Bash: 10, Read: 13, Edit: 6, Grep: 4, Glob: 1, Skill: 1). 17 unique files. No redundancy.\n\n### 15-3-driver-capability-matrix-routing-hints — verify (2026-04-03T13:40)\n\n- **AGENTS.md staleness:** `src/lib/AGENTS.md` and `src/lib/agents/AGENTS.md` missing `capability-check.ts`. Fixed.\n- **Pre-existing lint error:** `require-yield` in workflow-engine.test.ts:170 — not from story 15-3.\n- **Pre-existing 300-line violations:** codex.ts (333), opencode.ts (339) from stories 12-1/12-2. This story added 1 line each.\n- **Observation:** `codeharness drivers` CLI works in both pretty-print and JSON modes.\n- ALL_PASS: 12/12 ACs verified. `codeharness verify` passes after AGENTS.md fix.\n\nToken Report: 15 tool calls (Bash: 11, Read: 1, Write: 1, Grep: 1, Glob: 2). 1 unique file. Minor redundancy (2 duplicate CLI runs).\n"}}
