{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KhNnJdLftz2zQFW6Xewer3","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\tstepsCompleted: [1, 2]\n3\tstatus: complete\n4\tcompletedAt: '2026-04-03'\n5\tinputDocuments:\n6\t  - prd.md (parallel execution PRD)\n7\t  - ux-design-specification.md (existing CLI UX v2)\n8\t  - architecture-multi-framework.md (TUI component architecture)\n9\tworkflowType: 'ux-design'\n10\tnote: 'Multi-lane TUI UX for parallel epic execution, merge status, and telemetry visibility'\n11\t---\n12\t\n13\t# TUI UX Specification — Parallel Execution Extension\n14\t\n15\t**Date:** 2026-04-03\n16\t**Extends:** ux-design-specification.md (CLI UX v2)\n17\t\n18\t## Overview\n19\t\n20\tThis extends the existing CLI UX patterns for parallel execution. The core addition: the TUI goes from a single-lane view (one story at a time) to a **multi-lane view** (multiple epics executing concurrently in separate worktrees). All existing patterns (status prefixes, symbols, progressive detail, dense output) remain unchanged.\n21\t\n22\t**New UX surfaces:**\n23\t1. Multi-lane TUI rendering during `codeharness run --live`\n24\t2. Merge status and conflict resolution display\n25\t3. Lane lifecycle visualization (create → execute → merge → cleanup)\n26\t4. Telemetry visibility (optional, not in default view)\n27\t5. Updated `codeharness status` for parallel runs\n28\t\n29\t## Design Principles (Inherited + Extended)\n30\t\n31\tAll 8 existing principles apply. New additions:\n32\t\n33\t9. **Lanes are independent.** Each lane is self-contained — a failure in lane 1 doesn't pollute lane 2's display.\n34\t10. **Merge is a first-class event.** Merge attempts, conflicts, resolutions, and test results are visible — not hidden in logs.\n35\t11. **Parallel ≠ noisy.** Two lanes should be as readable as one lane was. Compress, don't duplicate.\n36\t\n37\t## Multi-Lane Live Mode: `codeharness run --live`\n38\t\n39\t### Two Parallel Lanes (Default: max_parallel=2)\n40\t\n41\t```\n42\tcodeharness run | 2 lanes | 47m elapsed | $18.60 spent\n43\t━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n44\t Lane 1: Epic 10 — Driver Interface         Lane 2: Epic 14 — TUI Workflow\n45\t 10-3 ◆ dev (AC 4/9)                        14-1 ◆ verify (AC 2/6)\n46\t ✓ 10-1  ✓ 10-2  ◆ 10-3  ○ 10-4  ○ 10-5   ◆ 14-1  ○ 14-2  ○ 14-3\n47\t claude-code | $4.20 / 18m                   codex | $1.30 / 8m\n48\t━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n49\tDone: 10-1 ✓  10-2 ✓ │ Merging: — │ Pending: epic-11, epic-12, epic-13, epic-15\n50\t━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n51\t ✓ Read src/lib/agents/drivers/types.ts\n52\t ⚡ Edit src/lib/agents/drivers/claude-code.ts ◌\n53\t```\n54\t\n55\t### Layout Rules\n56\t\n57\t**Header line:** `codeharness run | {N} lanes | {elapsed} | ${cost}`\n58\t\n59\t**Lane columns:**\n60\t- Two lanes render side-by-side (half terminal width each)\n61\t- Three+ lanes: top 2 active lanes shown, others collapsed to one-line summaries below\n62\t- Each lane shows: epic title, current story + phase + AC progress, story progress bar, driver + cost/time\n63\t\n64\t**Summary bar:** Between lanes and activity. Shows: done count, merge status, pending epics.\n65\t\n66\t**Activity section:** Shows the MOST RECENTLY ACTIVE lane's tool/thought/retry. Only one activity stream at a time — the one that last produced output. Prefixed with lane number.\n67\t\n68\t### Three or More Lanes\n69\t\n70\t```\n71\tcodeharness run | 3 lanes | 1h12m elapsed | $32.10 spent\n72\t━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n73\t Lane 1: Epic 10 — Driver Interface         Lane 2: Epic 14 — TUI Workflow\n74\t 10-4 ◆ verify (AC 3/7)                     14-2 ◆ dev\n75\t ✓ 10-1  ✓ 10-2  ✓ 10-3  ◆ 10-4  ○ 10-5   ✓ 14-1  ◆ 14-2  ○ 14-3\n76\t claude-code | $6.80 / 32m                   codex | $2.10 / 14m\n77\t━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n78\t Lane 3: Epic 11 — Workflow Schema │ 11-1 ◆ dev │ $0.40 / 2m\n79\t━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n80\tDone: 10-1 ✓  10-2 ✓  10-3 ✓  14-1 ✓ │ Merging: — │ Pending: epic-12, epic-13"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01T8UdeYWzSFyXWGbZbNGtaf","session_id":"9c9fe147-c536-4d36-9f64-8249f0c68839","uuid":"22496cb7-7738-4a65-b0fb-f13e63c4bf3e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:37:37.150Z"}
