th loop blocks correctly`\n78\t\n79\t## AC 6: `workflow-parser.ts` delegates to hierarchical-flow and exposes structure\n80\t<!-- verification: test-provable -->\n81\t\n82\t**Result: PASS**\n83\t\n84\t- **Code evidence:** `workflow-parser.ts` imports `resolveHierarchicalFlow`, `HierarchicalFlowError`, and type `HierarchicalFlow`. `ResolvedWorkflow` interface includes `execution`, `storyFlow`, `epicFlow` fields.\n85\t- **Test evidence:** 1 test passes:\n86\t  - `parses workflow with execution + story_flow + epic_flow`\n87\t\n88\t## AC 7: story_flow with dangling task reference is rejected\n89\t<!-- verification: test-provable -->\n90\t\n91\t**Result: PASS**\n92\t\n93\t- **Test evidence:** 2 tests pass:\n94\t  - `rejects story_flow referencing undefined task`\n95\t  - `rejects story_flow loop block referencing undefined task`\n96\t\n97\t## AC 8: epic_flow with non-built-in undefined task is rejected\n98\t<!-- verification: test-provable -->\n99\t\n100\t**Result: PASS**\n101\t\n102\t- **Test evidence:** 3 tests pass:\n103\t  - `rejects epic_flow referencing undefined non-built-in task`\n104\t  - `rejects epic_flow loop block referencing undefined non-built-in task`\n105\t  - `accepts epic_flow with built-in merge and validate (AC #8)`\n106\t\n107\t## AC 9: Coexistence of `flow:` and `story_flow:` is rejected\n108\t<!-- verification: test-provable -->\n109\t\n110\t**Result: PASS**\n111\t\n112\t- **Test evidence:** 2 tests pass:\n113\t  - `rejects coexistence of flow and story_flow (AC #9)` (resolveHierarchicalFlow level)\n114\t  - `rejects workflow with both flow: and story_flow:` (parseWorkflow integration level)\n115\t\n116\t## AC 10: `agent: null` accepted in task definition\n117\t<!-- verification: test-provable -->\n118\t\n119\t**Result: PASS**\n120\t\n121\t- **Schema evidence:** `agent` field uses `oneOf: [{ type: \"string\" }, { type: \"null\" }]`\n122\t- **Test evidence:** 2 tests pass:\n123\t  - `accepts agent: null in task definition` (schema level)\n124\t  - `parses task with agent: null` (integration level)\n125\t\n126\t## AC 11: `scope: per-epic` accepted in task definition\n127\t<!-- verification: test-provable -->\n128\t\n129\t**Result: PASS**\n130\t\n131\t- **Schema evidence:** `scope` enum is `[\"per-story\", \"per-run\", \"per-epic\"]`\n132\t- **Test evidence:** 2 tests pass:\n133\t  - `accepts scope: per-epic in task definition` (schema level)\n134\t  - `parses task with scope: per-epic` (integration level)\n135\t\n136\t## Test Summary\n137\t\n138\t- **hierarchical-flow.test.ts:** 43/43 passed\n139\t- **Total suite:** 4691/4692 passed (1 pre-existing failure in stats.test.ts, unrelated)\n140\t- **Coverage on hierarchical-flow.ts:** 100% statements, 100% branches, 100% functions, 100% lines\n141\t\n142\t## Files Changed\n143\t\n144\t| File | Status |\n145\t|------|--------|\n146\t| `src/schemas/workflow.schema.json` | Modified |\n147\t| `src/lib/hierarchical-flow.ts` | New |\n148\t| `src/lib/workflow-parser.ts` | Modified |\n149\t| `src/commands/run.ts` | Modified |\n150\t| `src/lib/__tests__/hierarchical-flow.test.ts` | New |\n151\t| `src/lib/__tests__/driver-health-check.test.ts` | Modified |\n152\t| `src/lib/__tests__/workflow-engine.test.ts` | Modified |\n153\t| `src/lib/__tests__/schema-validate.test.ts` | Modified |\n154\t\n155\t## Final Result\n156\t\n157\t**ALL_PASS (11/11 ACs)**\n158\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_0116174wQNpVuEKBqTmHzsQd","session_id":"9c9fe147-c536-4d36-9f64-8249f0c68839","uuid":"376e3d21-d3c8-4d97-af3c-c25f077c2fce","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:04:56.308Z"}
